				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>RustyCat wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Having 1 person available 24x7 means employing 5.  (No, you can't really work them 168 hours per week.  At least, not for very long.)
